N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 297.6 - Signing of City of New York earnings tax returns and other documents

State Regulations

Administrative Code of the City of New York, ยง
11-1918

The provisions of Part 153 of this Title with respect to
the signing of New York State income tax returns statements and other documents
shall also be applicable to the signing of City of New York earnings tax
returns and other documents. Notes
